gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Timberwolves 122, Rockets 95
gameRecap.excerpt: The Timberwolves defeated the Rockets, 122-95. Anthony Edwards recorded 24 points, five assists, and three rebounds for the Timberwolves, with Karl-Anthony Towns adding 22 points, eight rebounds, and six assists in the win. Jalen Green tallied 20 points, five rebounds, and two assists for the Rockets in the defeat. The Timberwolves improve to 25-9 in the regular season, while the Rockets fall to 17-16.
